President Muhammadu Buhari has extended his condolences to the Akinfenwa family on the demise of Senator Mojisoluwa Akinfenwa, a former national chairman of the Alliance for Democracy (AD), who died last Thursday in Ibadan at the age of 89. The post Buhari, Akande, Afenifere, others mourn Akinfenwa  appeared first on The Guardian Nigeria News – Nigeria and World News. Source: Guardian